author: hqucms
body:
A few technical updates to the TF models (e.g., remove nodes that are only used for training like `cpf_input_batchnorm/keras_learning_phase` from the graph, fix the DeepDoubleX models for batch inference). No change in the output is expected. Small (5-10%) speedup and slightly reduced model size.

The models are converted from the original Keras models using
https://github.com/hqucms/keras_to_tensorflow/blob/master/keras_to_tensorflow.py
title: Technical update to the DeepJet and DeepDoubleX TF models
